# Syntax: <path pattern> @owner1 @owner2
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ==================== CONSENSUS-CRITICAL PATHS ====================
# These paths gate blockchain consensus and MUST NOT change without:
# 1. Code owner approval
# 2. PR label: "consensus-change"
# 3. Passing parity tests (old hash == new hash)
# 4. Security audit (for major changes)

