# ==================== REVIEW POLICY ====================
#
# Consensus-Critical Changes:
#   - Require PR label: "consensus-change"
#   - Require code owner approval
#   - Must pass parity tests (determinism.yml)
#   - Must pass golden vector tests
#   - Recommended: security audit for major changes
#
# Security-Sensitive Changes:
#   - Require code owner approval
#   - Must pass security.yml workflow
#   - Must include threat model updates
#
# Dependency Updates:
#   - Require code owner approval
#   - Must pass cargo audit / pip-audit / govulncheck
#   - Must update SBOMs
#
# Emergency Hotfixes:
#   - Can bypass approval IF:
#     - Incident commander approval
#     - Post-merge review within 24h
#     - Post-mortem within 48h
#
# ==================== ESCALATION ====================
